During the epic battle of Sekigahara, two samurai face off outside of history. The heated duel between Kyoshiro and Demon Eyes Kyo is interrupted when a falling star slams down into the plains, shattering the geound and engulfing both of them. Years later, Kyoshiro, now a medicine man, wanders the land with a forgotten past. Hidden deep inside him is the soul of his old opponent, Kyo, slayer of a thousand men. When the bounty hunter Yuya and Kyoshiro are thrown into battle, the medicine man\\\&#039;s friendly personality retreats, and the world learns why Kyo is called a demon!
